Interface Information:Interface Type

Short name: Intf Type

Requires: Base Development System

Classes: I/O Session

Specifies the interface type of the given session.

Values

1 GPIB
2 VXI
3 GPIB-VXI
4 Serial
5 PXI
6 TCPIP
7 USB
9 FireWire
